cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.DB, cs.HC. 

This paper deals with entity-oriented search, which is a subfield of information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also involves natural language processing (cs.CL) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques to develop a scheme of entity intent categories and annotate queries. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of knowledge bases (cs.DB) and the interaction with services, which may involve human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
